MTU Plans Weighs Offer for Volvo Aero-Engine Unit, FTD Reports

-- B y   P a t r i c k   D o n a h u e
-- 
2011-12-01T20:24:10Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-12-01/mtu-plans-weighs-offer-for-volvo-aero-engine-unit-ftd-reports.html
MTU Aero Engines Holding AG  may make
an offer for  Volvo AB (VOLVB) ’s aero-engine subsidiary, Financial Times
Deutschland reported, without saying where it got the
information.  The Volvo unit could be sold for more than 800 million
euros ($1.01 billion), the newspaper said. An offer would be
MTU’s third for the business since 2007.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Patrick Donahue in Berlin at 
 pdonahue1@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
James Hertling at 
